Is it just me? Or has everyone who works here taken leave? I was walking down the way this morning, and I couldn't see anyone in their office? Maybe there was a meeting.... which means I'm incredibly late.

I... er.. have an apology to make. Kaiba, a public apology. I am sorry for being not so nice recently. Thankyou for the Kuribo... how come you've given it to me though? Just curious.

I had a quiet day today. didn't give me much work to do so i had a pretty laid back day. I might go and see Ryou later... he really doesn't seem to be alive. *sobs*.

Aw... <lj user="haxx0r_kaiba">.. I'm not quite sure what I'm supposed to do with this parcel. *shifts uneasily*.

Anyway. Where is Ryou? I miss him. *sobs*. Now I wish Kaiba would cheer up. I know we don't exactly get along, but if he managed to raise a smile *snigger* the work placemight be happier.

<lj user="Elsalhir"> has given me a lot of work to do. But i've hardly seen Yami recently. It's worrying. I fear Kaiba has relegated his usual mind state.

I'm sorry I just feel like having a lie down, Anzu to top everything off keeps ringing.

Hey! i found a new user icon! I have an overload of work to do. Just wanted to let everyone know they're invited to a party. Ok, maybe i'm making it up, but I'm going to try and convince teh l33d3r to have a work do.

Maybe we can see the true extent to her and Kaiba's relationship. *laughs*. Sorry if i'm causing offence to teh ph33rl3ss one. *bows*

Phew. Although the layout isn't done yet... it's kind of improved. Now. *searches for Bakura* I want a word with you Bakura. *pins up notice*.

*waves at Ryou and giggles*

Mmm. Yami and I sure had fun earlier. Tis a great shame we don't get more time to do such shenagnegans... not that that's spelt correctly! Hehehhe. I feel faint. It's way too hot.

I think... I'm going mad. I keep chewing things. I must be nervous. Surely i should be cheery?
I finally got a journal. Not that I didn't want to before, I just have a busy schedule. Yami of all people should know that! *waves at Yami*.
